<item>
            <title>[LU-5924] conf-sanity test_32b: list verification failed </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-5924</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for Andreas Dilger &amp;lt;andreas.dilger@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/e0f890fc-6aca-11e4-b203-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/e0f890fc-6aca-11e4-b203-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/d8c0083c-6aea-11e4-b203-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/d8c0083c-6aea-11e4-b203-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/51cd9a20-6abc-11e4-a7b0-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/51cd9a20-6abc-11e4-a7b0-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_32b failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt; 144115205255725214 -rwxr-xr-x 1 0 0  2011 1357749811 rsyslog
 144115205255725479 lrwxrwxrwx 1 0 0 20 1381266337 K50netconsole -&amp;gt; ../init.d/netconsole
+144115205255725479 lrwxrwxrwx 1 0 0 20 1381266337 K50netconsole -&amp;gt; ../init.d/netconsole
 144115205255725476 lrwxrwxrwx 1 0 0 20 1381266337 K69rpcsvcgssd -&amp;gt; ../init.d/rpcsvcgssd
+144115205255725476 lrwxrwxrwx 1 0 0 20 1381266337 K69rpcsvcgssd -&amp;gt; ../init.d/rpcsvcgssd
+144115205255725475 lrwxrwxrwx 1 0 0 20 1381266337 K85messagebus -&amp;gt; ../init.d/messagebus
 144115205255725475 lrwxrwxrwx 1 0 0 20 1381266337 K85messagebus -&amp;gt; ../init.d/messagebus
 144115205255725489 lrwxrwxrwx 1 0 0 20 1381266337 K87irqbalance -&amp;gt; ../init.d/irqbalance
+144115205255725489 lrwxrwxrwx 1 0 0 20 1381266337 K87irqbalance -&amp;gt; ../init.d/irqbalance
 144115205255725530 lrwxrwxrwx 1 0 0 20 1381266338 K50netconsole -&amp;gt; ../init.d/netconsole
conf-sanity test_32b: @@@@@@ FAIL: list verification failed
conf-sanity test_32b: @@@@@@ FAIL: test_32b failed with 1
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It looks like this is only failing on ZFS tests, so I suspect it may be related to the recent landing of &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/12582&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/12582&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: conf-sanity 32b&lt;/p&gt;</description>
